---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Government Organizations | Upfront" description="Upfront provides government agencies the tools to view comprehensive, accurate ECE data.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Comprehensive ECE Data for Government Organizations
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Upfront provides government agencies the tools to view comprehensive, accurate ECE data. By consolidating data across systems and giving providers intuitive tools to update their program information, Upfront makes it easier to match families with available care and see childcare supply and demand gaps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solutions -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">
        Transforming the Future of Childcare Data
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Modern Family Search for Every Program</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Consolidate every data source such as Licensing, Quality, Provider Data, and CCMS into a single database for families to access in a user-friendly search website.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Real-Time Childcare Desert Maps</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Our real-time childcare desert maps provide valuable insights into underserved areas, so you can make data-driven decisions to bridge the gap and ensure every family has access to quality childcare options.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">User-Friendly, Centralized Program Data</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Quickly gather vacancies, desired capacity, enrollment data from childcare providers through an intuitive provider portal.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">
        Hear from Our Customers
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-teal/30 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-brand-navy mb-4">
            "Technology should make lives easier — and that's exactly what Upfront does for Maryland families."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray font-medium">Executive Director, Maryland Family Network</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-xl p-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-teal/30 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-brand-navy mb-4">
            "Upfront was a partner on every level — taking families, providers, and data into consideration for every decision."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray font-medium">Founder, Operation Child Care</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Learn about North Carolina's New Automated Data Platform
      </h2>
      <a href="/case-studies/north-carolina" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal font-medium hover:underline">
        Read the Case Study
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
